# UIURLToLaunchScreenAssociations

**Property List Key**

The mapping of URL schemes to launch screen configurations.

## Discussion

Set the keys of this dictionary to the URL schemes that your app supports. Provide a value for each key that is the identifier, stored in the [doc://com.apple.bundleresources/documentation/BundleResources/Information-Property-List/UILaunchScreens/UILaunchScreenDefinitions/UILaunchScreenIdentifier] key, of one of the launch screen definitions in your [doc://com.apple.bundleresources/documentation/BundleResources/Information-Property-List/UILaunchScreens/UILaunchScreenDefinitions] array.

## Associations

- **UIDefaultLaunchScreen**: The default launch screen configuration.
